					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1147915#post-3786625</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1147915/scp-2393#post-3786625</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 01 May 2018 19:10:20 +0000</pubDate>
								<wikidot:authorUserId>1903381</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>In the Russian branch we have an object, <a href="http://scpfoundation.ru/scp-1322-ru">a very strange fat man with his daughter, who exist only on records</a>. He (and his &quot;daughter&quot;) only becomes &quot;real&quot; for their victims, who firstly suffer from tinnitus and then &quot;disappear from our reality&quot;. Although they don't exist outside records (except for their victims), lack of recording doesn't stop their actions. It's called &quot;paradox&quot; of the object in the article itself.</p> <p>Maybe existence of SCP-2393 may be considered something similar&#8230;</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
