					<![CDATA[
						 <p>It is quite a step up from the initial draft, i would say. I personally can't imagine dryads burning trees though.</p> <p>The greater implication is that there may be an entire subculture of trees that have upgraded themselves with human technology and seen as weird (though it feels more like New Age than witchcraft from my POV, but <em>they're</em> trees).</p> 
				 	]]>
